<h3><a href="/zs_prepare_ios"><u>Project: ZS Prepare</u></a></h3>
<br />
<h5>ZS Prepare is a free iPhone application which allows remote access to the Zombie Strategies supply location database.  The application comes complete with an 8 step guide for zombie preparation.  Android versions of the App will follow the release of ZS Prepare to the iOS platform.</h5>
<h4>Status: Beta Testing - Targeted Release Christmas 2010</h4>
