<h3><u>Project: Zombie Alert System (Z.A.S.)</u></h3>
<br />
<h5>The Zombie Alert System is a predictive zombie civil defense system which monitors for indications of a possible zombie apocalypse and can automatically alert users through multiple mediums. Registering for a <u><a href="/signup">free account</a></u> on Zombie Strategies ensures that you will be able to receive emergency zombie alerts once the system goes online.</h5>
<h4>Status: Active Development - Prototyping Completed</h4>